1 SECTION 2.(c) G.S. 115C-270.10(a) reads as rewritten:
2 "(a) Fee Schedule. – The State Board of Education shall establish by rule a schedule of
3 fees for professional educator licensure and administrative changes. The fees established under
4 this section shall not exceed the actual cost of providing the service. The schedule may include
5 fees for any of the following services:
6 (1) Application for demographic or administrative changes to a license.
7 (2) Application for a duplicate license or for copies of documents in the licensure
8 files.
9 (3) Application for a renewal, extension, addition, upgrade, reinstatement, and
10 variation to a license.
11 (4) Initial application for a new graduate from any recognized educator
