40 (f) Criminal History Check Documents Not Public Record. – All the information
41 received by the local board of education through the checking of the criminal history or by a
42 governing body or the State Board of Education in accordance with this section is privileged
43 information and is not a public record but is for the exclusive use of the local board of education
